"<option>-platformtheme</option> <replaceable>Thème-plate-forme</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify the platform theme."
msgstr "Définit le thème de la plate-forme."

#. Tag: term
#: man-qt6options.7.docbook:141
